sequenceDiagram
    participant Env as Backend .env flags
    participant API as FastAPI Settings + Middleware
    participant Modules as GET /v1/modules (unauthenticated)
    participant Web as Next.js Frontend
    participant Sidebar as Sidebar Component
    participant Guard as ModuleGuard Component
    participant Route as Protected API Route

    Note over Env,API: At process startup
    Env->>API: Load MODULE_*_ENABLED flags
    API->>API: Validate and store in FastAPI Settings

    Note over Web,Guard: On page load
    Web->>Modules: Fetch module list (no auth required)
    Modules-->>Web: [{code, enabled}, ...]
    Web->>Sidebar: Filter nav by enabled flags
    Sidebar-->>Web: Disabled module links hidden
    Web->>Guard: Render page content
    Guard-->>Web: ModuleDisabledState if disabled

    Note over Web,Route: API call to disabled module
    Web->>Route: Request to disabled module endpoint
    Route-->>Web: 403 MODULE_DISABLED

    Note over Env,API: To change flags
    Env->>API: Update .env + restart process
    API->>Modules: New flag state served immediately
